@startuml fig-S20-e3-states
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false

title S20 — Object Lifecycle State Machine

[*] --> Present : seed data or INSERT
Present --> Selected : QUERY or GET match
Selected --> Present : session returns to idle
Present --> Present : UPDATE commit\nrevision incremented
Present --> Deleted : DELETE commit
Deleted --> [*]
Present --> Missing : unknown key queried
Missing --> Present : valid key requested

legend right
  Notifications follow committed UPDATE and DELETE events
  Durable storage is the source of truth
  Watch state belongs to sessions, not objects
endlegend
@enduml
